2026-05-16T03:51:05.7206970Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7207837Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7268965Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7269865Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7271273Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7272400Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7273274Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-16T03:51:05.7274010Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
