2026-05-16T03:51:06.2683887Z 12    <!--
2026-05-16T03:51:06.2684271Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-16T03:51:06.2684634Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-16T03:51:06.2685335Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-16T03:51:06.2685709Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-16T03:51:06.2686141Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
